title: THE PASSAGE (2011) By Roberto Minervini
description:
THE PASSAGE (2011)
by Roberto Minervini

** This is the first installment of Minervini's award-winning Texas Trilogy, which comprises LOW TIDE (2012) and STOP THE POUNDING HEART (2013) **

Synopsis:
Three people come together by chance and take a road trip to West Texas, where their lives are forever changed.

Language: English, Spanish
Running time: 89 min
